# PyInstaller
#  Typically these are written by pyinstaller in the project directory
#  but we do want to commit the build scripts, just not the build artifacts or specs
#  unless needed. Wait, the project currently has build.bat and build.sh.
#  We should ignore *.spec files generated automatically, but let's keep PyInstaller cache and build outputs ignored.
*.manifest
*.spec

